<emphasis id="12D8758BDB572E69598E42E7763ACBA9" bold="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Ecuador</emphasis>
: 
<emphasis id="36D44A38193E9E4E4CB4BB56D2DC1D5D" bold="true" pageId="20" pageNumber="21">Ecuador:</emphasis>
Orellana, Tiputini Biodiversity Station, Rio Tiputini, Erwin Transect, 232m, &quot;0.63173°S, 76.14420°W,&quot; 23 October 1998 (T.L. Erwin, et al.)(NMNH: 117233, female).
