</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="5B8EFBC092C37591F528AEEAD6D43B7F" pageId="22" pageNumber="23" type="geographic distribution">
<paragraph id="CBC9CE779B64161098A96B788A703A0C" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Geographic distribution.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="C8BF208756BD596896060AAD37F4698A" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">
(
<figureCitation id="DA8B6D5783C3BCE569D008B4D3D714DB" captionStart="Figure 11" captionStartId="F7" captionText="Figure 11. Distribution map of the species of the piranha group." httpUri="https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/14830" pageId="22" pageNumber="23">Fig. 11</figureCitation>
